<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><x18tc:ThreadedComments xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main" xmlns:x18tc="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/spreadsheetml/2018/threadedcomments" xmlns:xltc2="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/spreadsheetml/2020/threadedcomments2" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships"><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E99" dT="2022-05-03T15:23:52.00" personId="{17a77095-1b96-4a1a-9210-531eea85b8bb}" id="{ce0c819d-69d9-4b16-a785-0604674654ac}" done="1"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">There are 3 Golden Seeds missing, there are 43 total (44 if you count the bugged one in Moghwin Palace). All are found under a Golden Sapling, their locations are 1) West of the Academy courtyard, 2) southwest of the Ravine-Veiled Village and 3) in Mountaintops East in a valley northeast of the Minor Erdtree.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E99" dT="2022-05-03T19:52:48.00" personId="{bd3c9ad9-82ad-4ae1-a8f6-c065395c8d3d}" id="{96849fd6-135c-4f2e-bb6a-300bf7518482}" parentId="{ce0c819d-69d9-4b16-a785-0604674654ac}"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">Ah thank you. I felt like some were missing from the wiki. I will add those.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E99" dT="2022-05-04T20:33:50.00" personId="{17a77095-1b96-4a1a-9210-531eea85b8bb}" id="{e9df554b-700d-4b85-950e-7bed02c81208}" parentId="{ce0c819d-69d9-4b16-a785-0604674654ac}"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">Yeah, I updated the wiki after figuring out which were missing there so Fextralife should be good now. Map Genie helped me figure out which were missing.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E182" dT="2022-05-03T13:11:45.00" personId="{17a77095-1b96-4a1a-9210-531eea85b8bb}" id="{b1f0adaf-2f72-43e4-992e-492a859c7aea}" done="1"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">There are 2 Lost Ashes missing, there are 14 total. The missing ones are one in Leyndell slums' sewer tunnels (not the one near the Sewer Gaol) and the other missing one is at the bottom of the Sellia Hideaway cave.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E182" dT="2022-05-03T19:56:43.00" personId="{bd3c9ad9-82ad-4ae1-a8f6-c065395c8d3d}" id="{c8fd3920-baaf-4427-9af6-862cf2aee4b6}" parentId="{b1f0adaf-2f72-43e4-992e-492a859c7aea}"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">I knew I shouldn't have trusted the wiki with these counts. I should have looked how many I had in game. I have 28 from two playthroughs so that checks out. Thanks for the correction!
Marked as resolved</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="K2" dT="2024-09-09T05:49:50.00" personId="{e0a213db-63b6-4adf-8272-442078122e38}" id="{8f2b3b8a-9cfd-4d2b-af83-e00b09d7b123}" done="0"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">1</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="K3" dT="2024-09-09T05:49:59.00" personId="{e0a213db-63b6-4adf-8272-442078122e38}" id="{c21d1027-e455-4a57-b42e-54d2bfc79911}" done="0"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">1</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E166" dT="2022-05-03T12:23:06.00" personId="{17a77095-1b96-4a1a-9210-531eea85b8bb}" id="{8aae57e3-9561-4551-a08b-1d5627c2901a}" done="1"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">There are two more Celestial Dew for a total of 10. There is a second one in Night's Sacred Ground and there also is one in Erdtree Sanctuary. I've updated Fextralife as well.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="E166" dT="2022-05-03T19:55:24.00" personId="{bd3c9ad9-82ad-4ae1-a8f6-c065395c8d3d}" id="{c4f5c937-3f45-4595-b325-7b3a1b19ac88}" parentId="{8aae57e3-9561-4551-a08b-1d5627c2901a}"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">Thanks for this, I will add those in.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="I2" dT="2022-05-03T13:14:09.00" personId="{17a77095-1b96-4a1a-9210-531eea85b8bb}" id="{fac32877-7d36-4140-b155-2446cee03db0}" done="1"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">Does not highlight when checked.</x18tc:text></x18tc:threadedComment><x18tc:threadedComment ref="I2" dT="2022-05-03T19:54:32.00" personId="{bd3c9ad9-82ad-4ae1-a8f6-c065395c8d3d}" id="{6ed9b8e7-0e9a-45de-b26a-c892bb52dad6}" parentId="{fac32877-7d36-4140-b155-2446cee03db0}"><x18tc:text xml:space="preserve">Yeah I realized this a little while ago. You must have an older version copied if its not fixed for you. Thanks for pointing it out though.
